❯ Create a simple home page for my own personal selfhosted cloud.

  It should say in the center using italic playright font from google fonts:
  "Welcome to Ruby Cloud"
  and then below it should say in a sans serif font of your choice "Your
  unreliable BUT extraordinarily fun cloud solution.


  Then the user should be able to scroll and cards should reveal with a
  scrolling aniation (reveal on scroll) there should be text in the cards. the
  cards should have a 18px border radius.

  The text:

  "Multiple services such as Immich, Linkwarden, Rybbit etc" (for this one
  prhaes it better and add some more fitting text, dont make up stuff we host
  besides that)

  "All servers are located in Switzerland and are compliant to the Swiss Laws"

  "Using only open source tools"

  "90% reliable, but who needs those 10% when in a hurry right?"

  then below when the usre scrolls there should be a text effect. There should
  be text BIG on the left side of the screen, reaching to the center.

  It should be grayed out but when the user scrolls down the scroll is hijacked
  and the words turn white on scroll. (for each scroll one word more) use
  adjacent libraries for this.

  The text should be: "In a world obsessed with uptime and reliability, we
  proudly offer something different: unmatched suspense.
  With Ruby Cloud, every login is an adventure. Will your files be there? Will
  the server respond? Nobody knows—not even us! Our impressive 95% uptime means
  there's always that thrilling 5% chance your data is currently enjoying an
  unexpected vacation.
  Think of it as Russian roulette for the digital age. One moment you're
  accessing your precious files, the next moment... well, let's just say
  spontaneity is our specialty. Some call it unstable. We call it living on the
  edge."


  Use this color scheme:

  primary background: 272728
  primary text: d3d0cb
  accent: #9FB1BC
  darker accent: 6e8898


  General design guidelines: Use a hyper modern design language, use border
  radius for cards. the focus is on a simple, minimal yet elegant website. Add a
  modern footer, make some data for it up.

  Use these styles for the footer: use tis
  data, just for the styles)
